Vice President Joe Biden issued a statement expressing his sadness over the passing of Arlen Specter, a former senator. Biden described Specter as a great senator who lived his life with dignity and courage. He considered Specter a friend and admired him for his political and physical courage. Specter never abandoned his principles and excelled when they were tested. Biden also extended his condolences to Specter's wife, Joan, and his children, Shanin and Stephen.